---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import ClickToPlayBilibili from "../../components/ClickToPlayBilibili.astro";
import { withBase } from "../../lib/paths";

const detroitUrl = new URL(withBase("/portfolio/detroit/"), Astro.site ?? Astro.url.origin).toString();
const detroitImage = new URL(withBase("/images/portfolio/detroit/cover.webp"), Astro.site ?? Astro.url.origin).toString();
const detroitStructuredData = {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "CreativeWork",
    name: "《底特律：化身为人》UE5 复刻",
    headline: "《底特律：化身为人》“来自死者”片段",
    description: "基于 Unreal Engine 5 的交互叙事片段复刻：角色控制、QTE、环境扫描、镜头与后期流程复盘。",
    image: detroitImage,
    url: detroitUrl,
    datePublished: "2025-01-01",
    keywords: ["UE5", "Interaction", "Blueprint", "Case Study", "Virtual Production"],
    creator: {
        "@type": "Person",
        name: "祝庆",
        alternateName: "Zhu Qing",
    },
};
---

<BaseLayout
    title="《底特律：化身为人》UE5 复刻 | 祝庆"
    description="基于 Unreal Engine 5 的交互叙事片段复刻：角色控制、QTE、环境扫描、镜头与后期流程复盘。"
    activePath="/portfolio"
    backgroundVariant="article"
    image={withBase("/images/portfolio/detroit/cover.webp")}
    preloadImage="/images/portfolio/detroit/cover.webp"
    structuredData={detroitStructuredData}
>
    <section class="case-hero">
        <img src={withBase("/images/portfolio/detroit/cover.webp")} alt="Detroit UE5 recreation cover" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" />
        <div class="case-hero__overlay" data-reveal>
            <a class="case-back-link" href={withBase("/portfolio")} data-i18n-cn="返回作品集 / Works" data-i18n-en="Back to Works">返回作品集 / Works</a>
            <span class="eyebrow" data-i18n-cn="UE5 交互复盘 / Case Study" data-i18n-en="UE5 Interactive Case Study">UE5 交互复盘 / Case Study</span>
            <h1>《底特律：化身为人》“来自死者”片段</h1>
            <p>一段围绕人物操控、动画播放、自定义 QTE 与关卡序列互动搭建的虚幻引擎交互式体验。</p>
            <div class="case-meta">
                <span>UE5 交互复刻</span>
                <span>Case Study</span>
                <span>2025.01</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <nav class="chapter-nav" aria-label="Case study chapters">
        <a href="#intro">项目背景</a>
        <a href="#video">演示视频</a>
        <a href="#gallery">场景截图</a>
        <a href="#tech">技术实现</a>
        <a href="#lessons">复盘</a>
        <a href="#credits">致谢</a>
    </nav>

    <main class="case-content">
        <section id="intro" class="case-section" data-reveal>
            <h2>项目内容介绍<span>01</span></h2>
            <div class="text-block">
                <p class="lead">本项目实现了人物操控、动画播放、自定义 QTE（快速反应事件）与关卡序列互动，目标是复刻《底特律：化身为人》中马库斯从废弃垃圾场坑洞中重获新生的片段体验。</p>
                <p>玩家将扮演马库斯（Markus），一位觉醒了自我意识的仿生人。在经历重重变故后，他被遗弃在荒芜的废弃垃圾场坑洞中，身体严重受损，四周散落着其他破损的仿生人部件。</p>
                <ol class="flow-list">
                    <li>玩家需要调查周围环境，帮助马库斯获得修复视觉所需的眼睛组件。</li>
                    <li>装备眼睛后，玩家可以通过点击鼠标右键扫描和观察附近可用的零件，逐步收集并修复自身。</li>
                    <li>完整收集视觉、听觉和维生组件后，马库斯即可爬出坑洞、获得新生，游戏至此结束。</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="video" class="case-section" data-reveal>
            <h2>演示视频<span>02</span></h2>
            <div class="video-wrapper">
                <ClickToPlayBilibili
                    bvid="BV18XApe2Efy"
                    title="Detroit UE5 recreation video"
                    poster={withBase("/images/portfolio/detroit/cover.webp")}
                    eyebrow="Demo Video"
                    heading="点击播放"
                    description="《底特律：化身为人》UE5 场景与交互复刻演示"
                />
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="gallery" class="case-section" data-reveal>
            <h2>场景截图<span>03</span></h2>
            <div class="masonry-grid">
                {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 8, 7, 9].map((item) => (
                    <img src={withBase(`/images/portfolio/detroit/${item}.webp`)} alt={`Detroit recreation screenshot ${item}`} loading="lazy" />
                ))}
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="tech" class="case-section" data-reveal>
            <h2>技术实现说明<span>04</span></h2>
            <div class="tech-grid">
                <article>
                    <h3>地图搭建</h3>
                    <p>场景基于 Blender 建模与精细的地编调整，实现 100% 自主搭建。</p>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <h3>QTE 交互系统</h3>
                    <p>通过蓝图（Blueprint）与关卡序列（Level Sequence）之间的深度通信，实现视图冻结、自定义按键映射与交互效果。</p>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <h3>场景物体扫描</h3>
                    <p>利用后处理材质、Niagara 粒子系统以及自定义深度通道，还原原作的扫描透视与发光轮廓特效。</p>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <h3>自定义角色动画</h3>
                    <p>融合运动匹配（Motion Matching）与自定义骨骼网格体匹配技术，尽量贴近原片中的角色运动节奏。</p>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <h3>动态材质</h3>
                    <p>实现材质亮度的动态改变，以及断肢恢复时的渐变材质效果。</p>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <h3>角色与动作表现</h3>
                    <p>综合应用动捕、面捕、MetaHuman 框架以及手动 K 帧完成关键表演。</p>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <h3>视频与 UI 引导</h3>
                    <p>通过序列帧优化缓解外部视频播放卡顿，并借助动态 Widget 动画实现流畅的功能与人物引导 UI。</p>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <h3>摄像机与环境系统</h3>
                    <p>配置后处理眼部亮度适应和相机晃动效果；天气系统基于 Ultra Dynamic Sky 进行了深度定制。</p>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <h3>声音系统</h3>
                    <p>基于声音总线控制，实现切换不同角色状态时的实时音频状态切换。</p>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <h3>布料模拟</h3>
                    <p>对角色服装进行了布料运算模拟，让近景动作中的服装表现更自然。</p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="lessons" class="case-section" data-reveal>
            <h2>遇到问题与开发心得<span>05</span></h2>
            <div class="lesson-list">
                <article>
                    <h3>面部蒙皮与骨骼绑定失败</h3>
                    <p>由于下载的自定义 RK200 模型极为不标准，我在 Maya 中尝试整整两天进行面部绑定均告失败。最终选择将面部动作通过 MetaHuman 实现，或用原片片段进行替代。</p>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <h3>手部动作捕捉精度限制</h3>
                    <p>曾尝试使用 Dollars Mono 进行手部动捕，但精度较低、抽搐明显，且难以利用其生成的 .bvh 文件。后转用 Cascadeur 进行动捕配合手 K，虽然不能捕捉手指且制作较慢，但最终发现手 K 出来的动作效果反而最好。</p>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <h3>Motion Matching 资产库过于庞大</h3>
                    <p>原本期望深度修改 Motion Matching 示例动画库以更贴近原片动作，但因动作库过于庞大复杂，时间有限未敢深度涉及。</p>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <h3>视频播放性能瓶颈</h3>
                    <p>UE 播放外部视频文件易产生卡顿。虽然通过将其全部转化为序列帧找到了最优解，但播放时仍消耗大量资源，导致原本 60fps 的文件在运行时掉至 24fps 以下。</p>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <h3>材质遮罩与 MetaHuman 限制</h3>
                    <p>由于时间关系和技术限制，未能完美做出模型衣服与皮肤之间的不完整剥落感及内部光源透光效果，且 MetaHuman 无法直接自定义衣服导入，留下了些许遗憾。</p>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <h3>灾难性硬件与项目崩溃</h3>
                    <p>项目开发期间经历无数次蓝屏、爆显存、内存及驱动崩溃。甚至一度导致项目文件损坏、Content 文件夹内资产丢失、模型消失。此经历让我深刻汲取教训，学会了及时备份。</p>
                </article>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="case-quote">多给我一些时间吧！我能做得更好 QAQ</blockquote>
        </section>

        <section id="credits" class="case-section" data-reveal>
            <h2>附录与致谢<span>06</span></h2>
            <div class="credits-grid">
                <article>
                    <h3>素材来源</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Fab & MetaHuman</strong> - Epic Games 官方素材及 Motion Matching 示例文件</li>
                        <li><strong>Markus Broken RK200 模型</strong> - Sketchfab，作者 Q.SARDOR</li>
                        <li><strong>《底特律：化身为人》原片片段</strong> - Quantic Dream</li>
                    </ul>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <h3>核心参考教程</h3>
                    <p><strong>UI 系统：</strong>果果CG、soth1s、JaysongShao。</p>
                    <p><strong>动画/动捕控制：</strong>A-peak_虚幻丰哥、产奶的黄药师、吃瓜大魔王_、机智的小忍、蓝饺子、小狐狸和秃头怪、ACG老师。</p>
                    <p><strong>开发与优化：</strong>UE4阿文、白泽有点忙、王刀CooL、Promi1440、UE五栋大楼。</p>
                    <p><strong>特效及其他：</strong>优莱卡嗷非秀、源木良音、游戏人YR、超气人嘟嘟酱、仰泳Young。</p>
                    <p><strong>工具链：</strong>小小效果、Huangjst、ChaseHWYY。</p>
                </article>
                <article class="thanks-card">
                    <h3>特别鸣谢</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>感谢指导老师 <strong>薛彤老师</strong> 的悉心教导。</li>
                        <li>感谢 <strong>于浩然</strong> 同学慷慨提供的优质声音素材。</li>
                        <li>感谢 B 站各大 UP 主上传分享的免费高质量教程。</li>
                    </ul>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="return-panel" data-reveal>
            <div>
                <span class="eyebrow" data-i18n-cn="更多作品 / More Works" data-i18n-en="More Works">更多作品 / More Works</span>
                <h2 data-i18n-cn="继续查看作品集" data-i18n-en="Continue Browsing Works">继续查看作品集</h2>
                <p data-i18n-cn="回到作品集大厅，查看更多影视后期、数字人与虚幻引擎相关项目。" data-i18n-en="Return to the works index for more post-production, digital-human, and Unreal Engine projects.">回到作品集大厅，查看更多影视后期、数字人与虚幻引擎相关项目。</p>
            </div>
            <a href={withBase("/portfolio")} data-i18n-cn="返回作品集" data-i18n-en="Back to Works">返回作品集</a>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="site-footer" data-i18n-cn="© 2026 祝庆 Zhu Qing" data-i18n-en="© 2026 Zhu Qing">© 2026 祝庆 Zhu Qing</footer>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .case-hero {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 10;
        min-height: 86vh;
        display: grid;
        align-items: end;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: #000;
    }

    .case-hero img {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        filter: brightness(0.43) contrast(1.13) saturate(0.82);
    }

    .case-hero::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background:
            linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(5, 5, 5, 0.94), rgba(5, 5, 5, 0.2) 46%, rgba(5, 5, 5, 0.68)),
            linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(5, 5, 5, 0.78), transparent 66%);
    }

    .case-hero__overlay {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        width: min(880px, 100%);
        padding: calc(var(--header-height) + 80px) var(--page-x) 12vh;
    }

    .case-back-link {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        width: fit-content;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.34);
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(5, 5, 5, 0.54);
        color: #fff;
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: 0.76rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        padding: 8px 13px;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: border-color 180ms ease, color 180ms ease, background 180ms ease;
    }

    .case-back-link::before {
        content: "\2190";
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        line-height: 1;
    }

    .case-back-link:hover {
        border-color: rgba(255, 94, 0, 0.58);
        background: rgba(255, 94, 0, 0.2);
        color: #fff;
    }

    .case-hero h1 {
        margin: 14px 0 18px;
        color: #fff;
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: var(--title-article);
        line-height: 1.06;
        letter-spacing: 0;
        text-wrap: balance;
    }

    .case-hero p {
        margin: 0;
        color: #d2d2d4;
        font-size: var(--text-lead);
        line-height: 1.78;
    }

    .case-meta {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 12px 18px;
        margin-top: 26px;
        color: #d4d4d8;
        font-size: 0.86rem;
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .case-meta span:not(:last-child)::after {
        content: "/";
        margin-left: 18px;
        color: var(--text-dim);
    }

    .chapter-nav {
        position: sticky;
        top: var(--header-height);
        z-index: 70;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: clamp(14px, 3vw, 34px);
        padding: 14px var(--page-x);
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        background: rgba(5, 5, 5, 0.82);
        backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    }

    .chapter-nav a {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.86rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 180ms ease;
    }

    .chapter-nav a:hover {
        color: var(--text-main);
    }

    .case-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 10;
        width: min(100%, 1040px);
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 74px var(--page-x) 100px;
    }

    .case-section {
        margin-bottom: 98px;
        scroll-margin-top: calc(var(--header-height) + 70px);
    }

    .case-section h2 {
        display: flex;
        align-items: baseline;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 24px;
        margin: 0 0 34px;
        padding-bottom: 16px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        color: var(--text-main);
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: var(--title-section);
    }

    .case-section h2 span {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16);
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: clamp(1.55rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
        font-weight: 760;
        line-height: 1;
    }

    .text-block p {
        margin: 0 0 1.55rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: var(--text-body);
        line-height: 1.88;
    }

    .text-block .lead {
        padding: 18px 22px;
        border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.035);
        color: #fff;
        font-size: var(--text-lead);
    }

    .flow-list {
        display: grid;
        gap: 12px;
        margin: 24px 0 0;
        padding: 0;
        list-style: none;
        counter-reset: flow;
    }

    .flow-list li {
        position: relative;
        min-height: 58px;
        padding: 16px 18px 16px 64px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: var(--bg-panel);
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.72;
        counter-increment: flow;
    }

    .flow-list li::before {
        content: counter(flow, decimal-leading-zero);
        position: absolute;
        top: 16px;
        left: 18px;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: 0.86rem;
        font-weight: 800;
    }

    .video-wrapper {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: #111;
    }

    .video-wrapper iframe {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        border: 0;
    }

    .masonry-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 18px;
    }

    .masonry-grid img {
        width: 100%;
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
        object-fit: cover;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 5px;
        filter: brightness(0.78) saturate(0.86);
        transition: transform 260ms ease, filter 260ms ease;
    }

    .masonry-grid img:hover {
        transform: scale(1.018);
        filter: brightness(0.94) saturate(0.92);
    }

    .tech-grid,
    .lesson-list {
        display: grid;
        gap: 18px;
    }

    .tech-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .tech-grid article,
    .lesson-list article {
        padding: 26px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: var(--bg-panel);
    }

    .tech-grid h3,
    .lesson-list h3 {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: var(--title-card);
    }

    .tech-grid p,
    .lesson-list p,
    .return-panel p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.96rem;
        line-height: 1.74;
    }

    .lesson-list article {
        border-left: 4px solid rgba(255, 102, 102, 0.72);
        background: rgba(28, 8, 8, 0.38);
    }

    .lesson-list h3 {
        color: var(--danger);
    }

    .case-quote {
        margin: 24px 0 0;
        padding: 20px 24px;
        border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        background: rgba(255, 94, 0, 0.06);
        color: var(--text-main);
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: var(--text-lead);
        line-height: 1.72;
    }

    .credits-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 18px;
    }

    .credits-grid article {
        padding: 26px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: var(--bg-panel);
    }

    .credits-grid h3 {
        margin: 0 0 14px;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-size: var(--title-card);
    }

    .credits-grid ul {
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 1.1rem;
    }

    .credits-grid p,
    .credits-grid li {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.96rem;
        line-height: 1.78;
    }

    .credits-grid strong {
        color: var(--text-main);
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .thanks-card {
        border-color: rgba(255, 94, 0, 0.24);
        background: rgba(255, 94, 0, 0.045);
    }

    .return-panel {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 28px;
        padding: 34px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 94, 0, 0.22);
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: rgba(255, 94, 0, 0.045);
    }

    .return-panel h2 {
        margin: 8px 0 10px;
